Title: FlowSorted.CordBloodCombined.450k
Description: The FlowSorted.CordBloodCombined.450k package contains data derived from Illumina HumanMethylation450K and Illumina HumanMethylationEPIC DNA methylation microarrays (Gervin K, Salas LA et al. under review), consisting of 263 blood cell references and 26 umbilical cord blood samples, formatted as an RGChannelSet object for integration and normalization using most of the existing Bioconductor packages.
